PXL_20240506_184233845.jpg.description: Black graphic t-shirt with humorous white text 'I ❤️ MEDIUM UGLY MEN' displayed across the chest. The shirt is unfolded, lying flat on a patterned rug with intricate geometric designs in shades of red, blue, and beige.

PXL_20240506_184250476.jpg.description: Pair of black rubber slides, displayed on a patterned rug. The slides feature a thick, ridged sole for enhanced grip and a wide strap for comfort. The brand logo is subtly embossed on the strap, showcasing minimalist design.

PXL_20240506_184306570.jpg.description: Hair styling kit displayed on a vibrant patterned rug. The kit includes a red curling iron with a black power cord, packaged styling wax, and two gray fabric hair scrunchies. Ideal for creating varied hairstyles effortlessly.

PXL_20240506_184333399.jpg.description: Collection of skincare products arranged on a colorful patterned rug. The set includes a bottle of Cetaphil Daily Facial Cleanser, Australian Gold Botanical SPF 50 Tinted Face Sunscreen, a Dove Down with the Thickness Body Butter, and a spray bottle of Hawaiian Tropic Body Mist. These products offer a comprehensive routine for skincare and sun protection.

PXL_20240506_184356990.jpg.description: Pair of used Shimano cycling shoes in black and gray with velcro fastening straps, shown next to a clear plastic bag containing various small metal bike cleats and tools. The shoes are displayed on an ornate patterned rug, suitable for an active cyclist looking for durable gear.

PXL_20240506_184416253.jpg.description: Set of four modern matte gray ceramic coffee mugs. The mugs are placed upside down, showcasing their sleek design and uniform color. They are displayed on a colorful, patterned rug, making them ideal for both everyday use and as a stylish addition to any kitchen.

PXL_20240506_184434935.jpg.description: Collectible 1:87 scale model of a Porsche Carrera GT, encased in a transparent plastic display box. The model car boasts intricate details and a glossy black finish, making it a perfect item for enthusiasts and collectors. Displayed on a patterned rug, the setup highlights the car's sleek design and craftsmanship.

PXL_20240506_184449739.jpg.description: Assortment of condiment tubes, including tubes of Colman's Mustard, Marmite Yeast Extract, and a generic brand black pepper, neatly arranged on a decorative rug. The items are positioned to display their labels, emphasizing the variety and specialty of the sauces and seasonings offered.

PXL_20240506_184456360.jpg.description: Assorted collection of electronic power adapters and cables, including various brands and specifications, tangled together. The items are laid on a colorful geometric patterned rug. Suitable for tech enthusiasts or anyone in need of replacement cables and adapters.

PXL_20240506_184510134.jpg.description: Plastic storage bin with lid, shown both closed and open. Inside, the bin contains boxes of Primode compostable trash bags, offering a practical storage solution for household items or disposables. The bin is displayed on a colorful patterned rug, highlighting its utility and simplicity.

PXL_20240506_184913196.jpg.description: Electric hair trimmer by Braun, featuring a vibrant blue and black design with a rubber grip. The trimmer includes a power cord and is showcased on a richly patterned rug. Ideal for personal grooming with precision and ease.
